data.description: Welcome Home . . . This spacious home sits on a generous 1-acre lot. Garage includes a separate living area. The home boasts large vaulted living room and family room, perfect for entertaining. Kitchen is well-appointed with island, corian counters, newer appliances, new flooring and pantry. Primary bedroom features separate vanities, a soaker tub, shower, new tile accents, and walk-in closet. Enjoy the outdoors on the covered front cedar deck or covered concrete patio. Backyard is fenced & landscaped for privacy. Updates include newer roof, new int&ext paint, newer furnace/heat pump, new flooring and new water heater. Additional features include paved driveway, storage shed, and concrete RV pad & power hook up.
